short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to easily add Eater lists to your Google Maps saved places

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds an "Add to Google Maps" button to Eater lists that you can click on which creates a list in Google Maps and adds the list of restaurants to it.
